"3 cups thinly sliced red onion (1 large onion)","3/4 cup riesling or other slightly sweet white wine","2/3 cup fresh orange juice (2 large oranges)","1/3 cup orange marmalade","2 teaspoons tamarind paste","1/2 teaspoon crushed red pepper","3 3/4 pounds bone-in turkey thighs, skinned","2 teaspoons five-spice powder","1 teaspoon salt","1 tablespoon canola oil","2 cups fresh Satsuma mandarin orange sections (about 7 oranges)","1 1/2 tablespoons cornstarch","  Sliced green onions (optional)"